<div class="alert alert-info">
	<h4 class="media-heading"><p>{l s='How to get your Facebook Pixel ID and configure your module?' mod='pspixel'}</p></h4>
	{l s='To create your Facebook pixel:' mod='pspixel'}
	<ul>
		<li><b>1.</b> {l s='Go to your' mod='pspixel'} <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ads/manager/pixel/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer">{l s='Facebook Pixel tab in Ads Manager.' mod='pspixel'}</a></li>
		<li><b>2.</b> {l s='Click Create a Pixel.' mod='pspixel'}</li>
		<li><b>3.</b> {l s='Enter a name for your pixel.' mod='pspixel'}</li>
		<li><b>4.</b> {l s='Check the box to accept the terms.' mod='pspixel'}</li>
		<li><b>5.</b> {l s='Click Create Pixel.' mod='pspixel'}</li>
	</ul>
<br>
{l s='The Pixel ID is a unique 15-number code associated to your Facebook pixel.' mod='pspixel'}<br>
{l s='Go to the module\'s configuration tab, add your Facebook Pixel in the dedicated field and click on Save.' mod='pspixel'}<br><br>

{l s='To check if your Facebook pixel is working properly, you can either make a test by going to a page where a pixel was placed on and ensure the event is reported in your Facebook Pixel page or install a free Chrome extension called' mod='pspixel'} <b><a href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/facebook-pixel/pixel-helper" target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer">{l s='Facebook Pixel Helper.' mod='pspixel'}</a></b><br><br>

{l s='Before you begin, please make sure your Facebook pixel is installed and Active.' mod='pspixel'}<br><br>
{l s='Also note that pixels won\'t reflect immediatlely on your Facebook account, it may take some time (between 1 and 2 hours).' mod='pspixel'}<br>
</div>

